Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy for OREON STUDIOS OYUN YAZILIM TEKNOLOJI TICARET AS
Last updated: [16/05/2024]
This Privacy Policy describes how OREON STUDIOS OYUN YAZILIM TEKNOLOJI TICARET AS (“OREON,” “we,” “us,” “our”) collects, uses, and shares information about you when you use our mobile games, applications, and website.
1. Introduction
OREON is committed to protecting your privacy. We understand the importance of safeguarding your personal information and are dedicated to ensuring its confidentiality and security. If you are under 16, please read this Privacy Policy with a trusted adult and ensure you understand it before using OREON Apps and Games. Our services are not intended for children under 16. We adhere to strict data protection regulations and continuously work to enhance our data protection practices.
2. Data Collection
Methods of Data Collection
We collect data through various methods to provide and improve our services. These methods include:
Direct submissions by users (e.0g., account creation, in-app purchases)
Cookies and similar technologies
Third-party tools and SDKs
Types of Data Collected
We collect different types of data to tailor our services to your needs. The types of data we collect include:
Personal identifiers (e.g., IP address, device ID)
Usage data (e.g., interaction with apps, in-game behavior)
Technical information (e.g., device model, OS, connection type)
We ensure that the data collected is relevant and necessary for the purposes for which it is intended.
3. Legal Basis for Processing
We process your data based on the following legal grounds:
Consent
Legitimate interest
Contract fulfillment
Compliance with legal obligations
By using our apps, users automatically consent to this privacy policy. We ensure that we have a legal basis for every instance of data processing and take necessary steps to obtain your consent when required.
4. Data Usage
We use your data for the following purposes:
Providing and improving services
Performing analytics and monitoring performance
Serving personalized advertisements
Sending marketing communications
Ensuring security and preventing fraud
We may also use your data to enhance user experience, troubleshoot issues, and conduct research and analysis to improve our services.
5. Data Sharing
We do not sell your personal information. We share data with third parties only with your consent, except where required by law. Data may be transferred to our headquarters in Turkey.
