6. User Rights
You have the right to:
Access your data
Rectify inaccurate data
Request data deletion
Withdraw consent
Data portability
To exercise these rights, contact us at info@oreonstudios.com. We are committed to addressing your requests promptly and transparently.
7. Data Deletion Request
You may request Oreon Studios to erase without undue delay your personal data when it is no longer necessary for Oreon Studios to retain such data.
In order for your data to be erased you can contact Oreon Studios by info@oreonstudios.com with request.
8. Data Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Our security practices include encryption, access controls, and regular security audits to safeguard your information.
9. Data Retention
We retain personal data only for as long as necessary for the purposes described in this policy. User-level data is not kept longer than 36 months, except for first-party analytics data, which may be stored for up to 72 months. We regularly review our data retention policies to ensure compliance with legal requirements and best practices.
10. Cookies and Tracking Technologies
We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance user experience and collect non-personally identifiable information.
Types of Cookies
Necessary cookies: Essential for providing services and ensuring security.
Performance cookies: Used for tracking website performance.
Targeting cookies: Used for personalized advertising.
You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings. For more information, please refer to our Cookie Policy.
11. Policy Updates
We will notify users of changes to this policy through our app and website. Users are encouraged to review the policy periodically. Significant changes will be highlighted, and we may seek additional consent for certain updates.
12. Additional Information
In the event of a legal issue, Turkish courts in Ankara are authorized. This Privacy Policy is governed by the laws of Turkey, and any disputes arising from it will be subject to the jurisdiction of Turkish courts.
13. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at info@oreonstudios.com. We are committed to resolving any concerns and providing additional information about our privacy practices.
By using OREON Apps and Games, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. We may update this policy from time to time, and changes will be posted on this page.
